          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Buffalo's proximity to Canada and major highways makes it a logistics hub. We cover trucking, warehouse, and distribution operations.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
            <li>• Trucking companies</li>
            <li>• Warehouse operations</li>
            <li>• Distribution centers</li>
            <li>• Moving companies</li>
            <li>• Fleet maintenance</li>
          </ul>
